axis2.name: Rework Rate
axis2.text:
AVG(CASE 
WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" IN (<%=Rework_Activities%>)) > 0 
THEN 1.0 
ELSE 0.0 
END)
